S T A T E O F R H O D E I S L A N D
IN GENERAL ASSEMBLY
JANUARY SESSION, A.D. 2025
____________
A N A C T
RELATING TO SOLEMNIZATION OF MARRIAGES
Introduced By: Representative Terri Cortvriend
Date Introduced: March 19, 2025
Referred To: House Special Legislation
It is enacted by the General Assembly as follows:
1 SECTION 1. Notwithstanding any other general or special law to the contrary, Nunzio
2 Pontillo may join Andrew Peter Carson and Christos Nelson Anastasopoulos in marriage within
3 the City of Newport, Rhode Island, on or about May 10, 2025. Nunzio Pontillo is hereby authorized
4 and empowered to join the foregoing persons in marriage pursuant to and in accordance with
5 Chapter 3 of Title 15 of the General Laws, entitled “Solemnization of Marriages.”
6 SECTION 2. This act shall take effect upon passage.
